1
00:00:00,390 --> 00:00:01,339
Previously on "The Originals"...

2
00:00:01,340 --> 00:00:02,409
You're Klaus' father?

3
00:00:02,410 --> 00:00:03,803
You can bring me back to life.

4
00:00:04,850 --> 00:00:06,220
Welcome to my hell.

5
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:07,830
You're all right.

6
00:00:07,870 --> 00:00:09,749
Have you dreamt of our father?

7
00:00:09,750 --> 00:00:10,799
I saw Mikael.

8
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,240
I've been dreaming of him, too.

9
00:00:12,450 --> 00:00:15,039
Your mother was clearly a very gifted witch.

10
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:16,259
Any way I do the math,

11
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:17,879
it ends with me and my guys dead,

12
00:00:17,880 --> 00:00:20,157
So whatever it is you got coming with the wolves,

13
00:00:20,187 --> 00:00:23,492
just know that I will fight until I am dead!

14
00:00:28,250 --> 00:00:29,608
Nice job.

15
00:00:29,638 --> 00:00:32,480
You saved me the trouble of killing all these vampires myself.

16
00:00:35,082 --> 00:00:37,040
That baby is part witch.

17
00:00:37,070 --> 00:00:40,009
She has to be born first before she can die.

18
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:40,609
No!

19
00:00:40,610 --> 00:00:41,699
This the way it had to be.

20
00:00:41,764 --> 00:00:43,455
No!

21
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:56,451
Writing a love letter to one of your many suitors?

22
00:00:56,743 --> 00:00:59,270
So who's the lucky recipient then--

23
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:03,284
Jackson or Elijah?

24
00:01:03,870 --> 00:01:06,914
Don't tell me it's me.

25
00:01:06,944 --> 00:01:09,300
I thought I was out of the running ages ago.

26
00:01:09,310 --> 00:01:13,394
And the award for biggest ego goes to...

27
00:01:15,272 --> 00:01:16,728
Oh...

28
00:01:21,253 --> 00:01:23,177
How is our littlest wolf?

29
00:01:24,436 --> 00:01:26,342
Do you want to...

30
00:01:32,850 --> 00:01:34,532
Come on.

31
00:01:49,786 --> 00:01:51,438
You feel that?

32
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,647
Right.

33
00:02:00,781 --> 00:02:04,621
I'll leave you to your secret letter then.

34
00:02:13,610 --> 00:02:15,334
"Dear Zoey...

35
00:02:16,510 --> 00:02:19,960
"or Caitlin or Angela.

36
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:22,365
"To my little girl,

37
00:02:23,070 --> 00:02:26,097
"your dad just asked if this was a love letter.

38
00:02:27,130 --> 00:02:28,877
I guess it kind of is."

39
00:02:32,417 --> 00:02:34,642
"I never got to know my mother.

40
00:02:35,102 --> 00:02:38,060
"I have no idea what she must have felt when she carried me."

41
00:02:38,090 --> 00:02:40,447
Let go of me, you bitch!

42
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:43,500
"So I thought I'd write to you

43
00:02:43,530 --> 00:02:47,936
"so that you could know how happy I am at this very moment,

44
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:51,363
"Hh your father and I can't wait to meet you."

45
00:02:54,363 --> 00:02:56,551
"And I want to make you a promise,

46
00:02:56,581 --> 00:02:59,659
"3 things that you will have that I never did--

47
00:03:00,313 --> 00:03:02,266
"A safe home,

48
00:03:02,388 --> 00:03:06,604
"someone to tell you that they love you every single day,

49
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:11,609
and someone to fight for you no matter what."

50
00:03:11,930 --> 00:03:14,420
"In other words, a family.

51
00:03:14,581 --> 00:03:16,271
"So there you go, baby girl.

52
00:03:16,301 --> 00:03:19,020
"The rest we're gonna have to figure out together.

53
00:03:26,275 --> 00:03:29,289
You should know this brings me no joy.

54
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:31,861
I promise I'll make it quick.

55
00:03:32,748 --> 00:03:34,080
Let's begin, shall we?

56
00:03:34,110 --> 00:03:35,604
No, no!

